line: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">The Henderson</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">全新空間亦令我們得以透過多元展覽及活動與藏家深入互動，包括在亞洲首次舉行的日內瓦鐘錶大賞展覽、『迪拜鐘錶週』重要項目：鐘錶論壇，以及佳士得第九屆『</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">Art+Tech</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">藝術科技峰會』等。我們十分期待於</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">2025</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">年在新總部推出全年不間斷的藝術及精品拍賣與精彩活動，在亞洲這一重要的國際平台繼續為全球藏家與愛好者帶來無與倫比的體驗。</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important;">」</em></p><p><br/></p>','1');
