px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">億</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">美元</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">1.08</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">億</span>。<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">總體成交項目比率</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">92%</span>，<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">落槌總額為低估價</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">106%</span>。本季取得的斐然佳績見證佳士得專家團隊精心策劃的拍賣滿足廣大雅逸精品藏家的多元喜好，同時鞏固佳士得即將引領2024年<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">亞洲精品拍賣市場</span>的強勁勢頭。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">我們將亞太區總部遷至The Henderson的創舉成功令佳士得以更有活力的方式與藏家互動。本季拍賣的買家來源見證我們的影響力日益深入，新買家總數與2023年秋季相比增長32%（現場與網上拍賣總計新買家增長74%）。本季約三分之一買家為首次參與佳士得拍賣，逾半數買家為千禧新世代，見證我們成功吸引新一代年輕買家參與拍賣。可圈可點的是，亞太區買家貢獻總額與2023年秋季相比增長16%，東南亞買家貢獻增長達138%，日本和台灣買家貢獻分別增長182%和124%，彰顯區內藏家熾熱需求和購藏實力。今季取得的斐然佳績鞏固佳士得對雅逸精品市場的強大信心。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">數碼平台是本季藏家參與競投的重要方式，52%買家透過網上平台投得藏品，拍賣現場直播吸引逾670萬觀眾登入收看。拍賣吸引來自全球六大洲59個國家的買家積極參與。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">佳士得The Henderson亞太區新總部的博物館級藝廊現已成為藝術與精品藏家的首選目的地。三場精彩活動亦於十月在佳士得拉開帷幕，包括日內瓦鐘錶大賞（GPHG）、第十屆鐘錶論壇（Horology Forum）及第九屆Art+Tech藝術科技峰會，均吸引大量訪客蒞臨參加並獲得熱烈反響，足以見證佳士得The Henderson嶄新空間為世界頂級藝術與精品的殿堂，匯聚全球藏家於此溝通對話。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">不久後，我們將於11月7日在上海舉辦二十及二十一世紀晚間拍賣，並於11月9日在香港舉辦二十及二十一世紀日間拍賣，隨後將於11月末（27至29日）隆重舉辦新總部首屆亞洲藝術拍賣週。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">佳士得香港</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">|&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">雅逸精品系列拍賣佳績一覽</span></p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 630.992px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">珍罕名釀及烈酒</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border