gin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">香港</span>—佳士得欣然宣布於香港The Henderson的全新亞太區總部舉行<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">首個亞洲藝術週</span>，並於<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">2024年11月29日</span>呈獻<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">四場中國瓷器及工藝精品現場拍賣</span>，包括稍早公布的<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">「嘉木留芳─『木趣居』精選明式家具」</span>專場現場拍賣。精彩紛呈的拍賣萃選各地來源非凡的重要罕見珍藏，四場拍賣的總低估價逾港元3.5億。</p><hr style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px; text-wrap: wrap;"/><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">帕默家族典藏中國藝術</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">佳士得於2023年5月推出歐洲舉足輕重的帕默家族私人珍藏拍賣，成績斐然，今秋有幸再度呈獻<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">「帕默家族典藏中國藝術」</span>專場拍賣，帶來家族幾代成員歷經90餘載悉心蒐羅的藝術珍品，包括清代御瓷、明代青花瓷器、明清玉器和琺瑯器，部分珍藏更曾於1951年倫敦東方陶瓷學會舉辦的展覽中展出。這個珍稀出眾的私人珍藏充分展現帕默家族對收藏藝術的熱誠和鑑賞慧眼。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">這場專拍的領拍之作為一件<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">清乾隆青白玉御題詩雙魚如意洗「乾隆年製」隸書刻款</span>（封面左圖），這件難得一見的珍品經考證為兩件採用雙魚造型的清乾隆玉洗之一，背面刻有御題詩及乾隆最喜愛的兩方印文。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">其他精彩拍品包括：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/11671739022994.png" width="594" height="321"/><span style="font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; font-size: 14.6667px; text-wrap: wrap;"><br/><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">太一精魄</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">─</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">藍田山房舊藏古玉</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">「太一精魄─藍田山房舊藏古玉」</span>單一藏家專場現場拍賣呈獻<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">75</span>件來自台灣著名<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">藍田山房舊藏</span>的古玉珍品，展現中國古玉自新石器時代至東漢數千年間的發展及變化。75件拍品皆曾在1999年台北故宮博物院「羣玉別藏續集」特展中展出，其後未有再公開展示至今。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">領拍之作為<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">西漢綠松石辟邪圓雕</span>（封面右圖），乃迄今所見尺寸最大、雕工最生動細緻的辟邪圓雕之一，也是唯一以綠松石雕刻的碩大珍品。早於新石器時代晚期，綠松石已是中國藝術品的重要創作元素，但一般用作鑲嵌裝飾，鮮有製成圓雕。這件獨特的辟邪印證漢朝工匠的非凡技藝，能以巧手將珍貴的綠松石雕琢成形態生動的傑作。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">其他矚目拍品還有全球僅有12件的<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">良渚文化鳥立祭壇紋玉璧</span>（下左圖），以及衆多難得一見的古玉珍品：</p><p><br/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/49841739022994.png" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/96591739022995.png" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/33751739022995.png" width="594" height="321"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">重要中國瓷器及工藝精品</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">今年11月，佳士得The Henderson全新亞太區總部舉行的橫跨三個月的開幕系列拍賣將由壓軸登場的<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">重要中國瓷器及工藝精品</span>畫上完美句點。本場拍賣悉心蒐羅<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">150</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">餘件</span>出類拔萃的中國瓷器珍品，橫跨西周至民國時期。種類多元的瑰寶包括來自各地顯赫私人珍藏的宋瓷、明清御瓷、漆器、中國古典家具、御製玉璽和文房珍玩，全部均來源有緒，彌足珍貴。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">領銜之作為一件<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">明宣德青花吹簫引鳳圖盌</span>（封面中圖），此盌於景德鎮御窯為宮廷燒製，完美體現這段瓷器製作工藝全盛時期的頂尖技藝和卓越品質。盌上細緻生動的青花紋描繪《吹簫引鳳》的故事，為宣德年間深受歡迎的吉祥題材，象徵明君治國、盛世太平的祝願。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">其他精選拍品亦包括<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">清乾隆粉彩百鹿雙耳尊</span>（下方左圖）、<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">清乾隆紫檀圓包圓裹腿畫桌一對</span>（下方第二行）、一對金釉地金彩山水紋碗，以及38件<span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">藝德堂珍藏</span>御瓷和工藝精品。</p><p><br/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/47171739022997.png" width="594" height="321"/><img src="http://wmiw.ebnnw.cn/Public/ueditor/php/upload/74831739023005.png" width="594" height="321"/><img src="https://christies.epresspack.me/storage/clients/641/imagetools0_1728872751.png" width="594" height="321"/></p>','1');
