0.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">2024&nbsp;</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">年初至今</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;">在充滿挑戰的宏觀經濟環境下，佳士得於2024年上半年取得美元21億的全球拍賣成交總額，期內全球最高成交價的10件藝術品當中，佳士得拍出六件，同時呈獻六個重要珍藏，拍賣成交比率為87%，落搥價總額為低估價111%，彰顯佳士得隱固的市場領導地位。踏入下半年，佳士得已在倫敦拍場以超過美元1,300萬拍出兩件刷新紀錄的古典大師作品，並宣布將於9月在紐約舉辦創新的系列拍賣，呈獻保羅·艾倫的珍藏傑作，以及公布在巴黎、倫敦、紐約及香港舉辦大型二十及二十一世紀藝術拍賣的計劃，令人期待。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14.6667px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; width: 390.435px; font-family: &quot;ABC Arizona Serif&quot;, serif; text-wrap: wrap; line-height: 1.35em !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">2024</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: 0px; text-transform: inherit !important; font-weight: 700 !important;">年上半年全球拍賣數據</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: 0.3s ease-in; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1