INSERT INTO `on_news` VALUES ('61','18','博物館和企業收藏服務','','博物館和企業收藏服務','','1','概述三十多年來，佳士得一直是與博物館、非營利機構和企業收藏合作的領導者。我們是第一家成立部門專門滿足這些組織獨特需求的拍賣行。我們經驗豐富的團隊與大大小小的機構合作，包括歷史學會、圖書館、大學和藝術博物館——包括百科全書式和小眾機構。我們處理各種規模和主題的專案，從單件物品到大型收藏品，從古董到歷史手稿，從裝飾藝術到當代藝術。我們很榮幸能夠通過收購幫助機構塑造他們的收藏，並很自豪能與他們合作，為他&hellip;','1740403466','1740403466','<p><span style="font-size: 36px; text-decoration: underline;"><a class="chr-page-nav__link " href="https://www.christies.com.cn/services/museum-and-corporate-collection-services/overview" data-title="Overview" _msttexthash="6290102" _msthash="22" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 4px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; padding: 0px 0px 4px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; touch-action: manipulation; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); text-transform: uppercase; transition-duration: 0.3s; transition-property: border, color; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.39, 0.58, 0.57, 1); display: inline-block; position: relative; cursor: pointer;">概述</a></span><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: ABCArizonaSerif; font-size: 1.25rem;">三十多年來，佳士得一直是與博物館、非營利機構和企業收藏合作的領導者。</span></p><p class="chr-rich-text__body" _msttexthash="17904312608" _msthash="27" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.4; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我們是第一家成立部門專門滿足這些組織獨特需求的拍賣行。我們經驗豐富的團隊與大大小小的機構合作，包括歷史學會、圖書館、大學和藝術博物館——包括百科全書式和小眾機構。我們處理各種規模和主題的專案，從單件物品到大型收藏品，從古董到歷史手稿，從裝飾藝術到當代藝術。<br _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>我們很榮幸能夠通過收購幫助機構塑造他們的收藏，並很自豪能與他們合作，為他們在拍賣會或私人銷售中提供的作品取得非凡的成果。我們還致力於與機構客戶合作，通過教育活動和計劃培養他們的顧客，並幫助他們參與社區並實現籌款目標。我們的團隊在該領域擁有近50年的綜合經驗，是拍賣業務中經驗最豐富的團隊。請隨時與我們聯繫，詳細瞭解我們的服務如何量身定製以滿足您機構的需求。</p><p><span style="font-size: 36px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"></span><a class="chr-page-nav__link chr-page-nav__link--active" href="https://www.christies.com.cn/services/museum-and-corporate-collection-services/what-we-offer" data-title="What we offer" _msttexthash="22093474" _msthash="23" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 4px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: currentcolor; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; padding: 0px 0px 4px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; touch-action: manipulation; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); text-decoration-line: none; text-transform: uppercase; transition-duration: 0.3s; transition-property: border, color; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.39, 0.58, 0.57, 1); display: inline-block; position: relative; cursor: pointer;">我們提供的服務</a></span><br/></p><p><br/></p><p class="chr-rich-text__intro" _msttexthash="2095891525" _msthash="26" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 40px 0px 24px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 20px; font-family: ABCArizonaSerif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 1.25rem; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我們認識到每個機構都是獨一無二的。我們的團隊實施了在我們數十年的歷史中磨練的最佳實踐，我們明白每個專案的範圍和目標是單一而具體的。因此，我們根據您的特定需求量身定製解決方案，指導您完成整個過程的每一步。</p><p class="chr-rich-text__body" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.4; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">銷售協助</span><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>我們在市場上展示您的藝術品以最大限度地發揮其潛力，同時與您合作，確保在銷售過程中傳達反映您目標的明確資訊。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><span _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">協助購買無論是</span><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>拍賣還是私人銷售，我們的團隊都會與您合作，以確保簡化收購流程。我們保留「願望清單」 以便在相關作品出現在市場上時提供慷慨的提前通知。我們瞭解世界各地的私人收藏藝術品，並經常與可能有興趣私下出售給機構的收藏家接洽。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><span _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">財務機會</span><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>我們提供一系列財務選擇，方便機構在佳士得購買。除了延長付款套餐外，我們還可以通過佳士得藝術金融和第三方擔保機會向機構提供優惠貸款條件。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><span _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">估價</span><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>佳士得為各種目的提供估價，包括保險和財務規劃的公允市場價值。此外，我們還為聯邦賠償流程提供説明。我們的博物館服務團隊每年都會處理大量賠償評估，最近的亮點包括<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">Mary Cassatt在</em>費城藝術博物館工作;舊金山美術博物館的<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">波提切利素描展</em>;<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">楓丹白露的畢卡索</em>，現代藝術博物館;以及大都會藝術博物館的&nbsp;<em _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">Van Gogh Cypresss</em>。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><span _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">特別活動和專案</span><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>佳士得提供廣泛的節目，以滿足您機構的個人化需求。我們世界各地的專家定期參加博物館和大學的虛擬和面對面講座和研討會，其中許多人還擔任慈善拍賣師，每年幫助籌集數百萬美元以支援各種事業。我們經常接待博物館團體進行獨家導覽，與博物館工作人員合作，為頂級顧客舉辦定製活動和網路研討會，並確保訪問全球私人收藏進行獨家導覽。我們還在佳士得、在線或貴機構合作舉辦籌款活動，並在世界各地的畫廊和會議室舉辦博物館董事會會議。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><a href="https://www.christies.com.cn/about/philanthropy/overview" _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; touch-action: manipulation; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); transition-duration: 0.15s; transition-property: color; transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.39, 0.58, 0.57, 1);">促進慈善事業</a>佳<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>士得很榮幸能通過我們的網路支持機構的慈善活動，包括促進藝術品銷售以造福重要事業;在可能的情況下，提供我們的拍賣室作為籌款活動的場所;或提供專業的慈善拍賣師。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><span _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">研究和銷售渠道</span><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>我們圖文並茂、研究非常充分的銷售資訊可以作為有用的參考資料，為即將舉行的展覽提供學術背景或用作未來收購的指南。我們的團隊可以安排免費進入您選擇的收藏類別。<br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><span _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit;">促進貸款申請佳</span><br _mstmutation="1" _istranslated="1" style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>士得擁有無與倫比的全球頂級收藏家網路，我們與這些收藏家建立了牢固的關係。我們很高興利用這個位置為即將到來的展覽尋找作品的機構與有興趣將其藝術展出以豐富公眾和享受的收藏家牽線搭橋。</span></p><p><a class="chr-page-nav__link " href="https://www.christies.com.cn/services/museum-and-corporate-collection-services/institutional-partners" data-title="Institutional partners" _msttexthash="16879096" _msthash="24" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 4px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; padding: 0px 0px 4px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: ABCArizonaSans; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-